01:06:09.000 --> 01:06:10.000
Bill?

685
01:06:10.750 --> 01:06:11.834
Que bom que ligou.

686
01:06:12.417 --> 01:06:14.292
Sabia que ligaria.

687
01:06:14.459 --> 01:06:15.459
Sabia, Bill.

688
01:06:18.167 --> 01:06:20.167
