733
01:14:06.125 --> 01:14:07.125
Margot, empurre.

734
01:14:11.917 --> 01:14:12.917
Está vindo.

735
01:14:15.042 --> 01:14:16.042
Calma.

736
01:14:55.500 --> 01:14:56.500
Meu Deus.

737
01:14:56.959 --> 01:14:57.959
